{"tid":831605,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米上架 XR/XS/XS Max 套装，諷刺 Apple 手機價格離地","createTime":"2018-09-22T05:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T05:28:37.000Z","uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"82155a43973cf3b9dd6c8cca96a523d7ab35cb9e","tid":831605,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/135649_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F135649_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9a664b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在9月13日，Apple 在秋季發布會給我們發布了三款新iPhone，分別是 iPhone XR、iPhone XS 和 iPhone XS Max，他們的價格都不便宜呀！起售價分別是HK$6499、 HK$8599和HK$9499元。超乎人們的意料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/135706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F135706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ec8dc13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於這個高昂的價格，在9月19號，小米商城悄悄的上架了 XR套裝、XS套裝 和 XS Max套裝，不僅僅命名與新款 iPhone 一樣，而且價格上也是一致的(對比中國版 iPhone 價格)。但是小米商城賣的套餐不僅僅是手機，還包含了一系列產品。像是在嘲諷著 Apple 這個價我們已經買到很多產品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/135723_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F135723_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8b241001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在最便宜的 XR套裝中，總共包含了小米8 SE 6GB+128GB深灰版、小米手環3、小米筆記本Air 12.5吋 4GB+256GB銀色和小米藍牙耳機mini 黑色四件電子產品，售價僅和 中國 iPhone XR 64GB版本一樣， 6499元人民幣。瞬間感覺到了 iPhone 的高貴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/135737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F135737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3ca1dae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個套餐是 XS套裝，其中包含小米MIX 2S 8GB+256GB黑色尊享版、小米手環3、小米筆記本Air 13.3吋四核銀色增強版和小米藍牙耳機mini 也是四件電子產品，售價和中國版 iPhone XS 64GB售價一致，為8699元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/135747_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F135747_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=edef48e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後最為昂貴的 XS Max 套裝版包含小米8 6GB+128GB版本、小米筆記本Pro、小米藍牙項圈耳機和小米手環3等電子產品，售價僅為中國 iPhone XS Max 64GB版本的 9599元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n小米通過這一輪的價格對比，確實讓我們體驗到了新款 iPhone 的貴氣"},{"pid":"33c7ceb7d249a503779a057e1ae49f4463e711aa","tid":831605,"uid":77569,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05f75eb54125174c9ab82613265070ef62529b25","tid":831605,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"名都唔使諗又有得見報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1af551e817eb21a54ebe25435ce8a3e719c0f22","tid":831605,"uid":55571,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"小米個垃圾an 狗也不_ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb8a4d9d8f06202dda26fc4f0ada9376bc3a2dc","tid":831605,"uid":33730,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"連型號都抄, 仲好意思話諷刺<br />\n要幾低賤既人先會買小米"},{"pid":"439d20ad6d2ec24c591067906ca49cd0ff057ca4","tid":831605,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"0fb8a4d9d8f06202dda26fc4f0ada9376bc3a2dc","tid":831605,"uid":33730,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"連型號都抄, 仲好意思話諷刺<br />\n要幾低賤既人先會買小米"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:15:27.000Z","msg":"小米max都係抄xs max 小米真仆街"},{"pid":"3fcea4a26ce8b840e54451a4784ec6467f36fa7a","tid":831605,"uid":33730,"like":7,"